                            Based on the context: talk start time:8:56 pm on 20 July, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Thanks, Melanie! It's awesome to have our own platform to be ourselves and support others' rights. Our group, 'Connected LGBTQ Activists', is made of all kinds of people investing in positive changes. We have regular meetings, plan events and campaigns, to get together and support each other.memory context: a photo of a painted sidewalk with a rainbow design on itmemory keywords: []memory tags: ['inclusive', 'diverse', 'community', 'symbolism', 'emotional']
talk start time:1:56 pm on 8 May, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : I went to a LGBTQ support group yesterday and it was so powerful.memory context: Speaker Carolinesays : I went to a LGBTQ support group yesterday and it was so powerful.memory keywords: []memory tags: ['general']
talk start time:1:33 pm on 25 August, 2023memory content: Speaker Melaniesays : Wow, Caroline, that's awesome! Can't wait to see your show - the LGBTQ community needs more platforms like this!memory context: Generalmemory keywords: []memory tags: ['general']
talk start time:1:14 pm on 25 May, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : I chose them 'cause they help LGBTQ+ folks with adoption. Their inclusivity and support really spoke to me.memory context: Generalmemory keywords: []memory tags: []
talk start time:7:55 pm on 9 June, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Hey Melanie! How's it going? I wanted to tell you about my school event last week. It was awesome! I talked about my transgender journey and encouraged students to get involved in the LGBTQ community. It was great to see their reactions. It made me reflect on how far I've come since I started transitioning three years ago.memory context: Speaker Caroline says : Speaker Melaniesays : Wow, Caroline, sounds like the parade was an awesome experience! It's great to see the love and support for the LGBTQ+ community. Congrats! Has this experience influenced your goals at all?memory keywords: []memory tags: ['inclusive', 'community', 'general']
talk start time:2:31 pm on 17 July, 2023memory content: Speaker Melaniesays : Wow, Caroline! They must have felt so appreciated. It's awesome to see the difference we can make in each other's lives. Any other exciting LGBTQ advocacy stuff coming up?memory context: Speaker Carolinesays : Wow, your kids had so much fun at the park! Being outdoors can be really enjoyable. A lot happened since our last chat. I've been chasing my ambitions and had the chance to volunteer at an LGBTQ+ youth center. I'm giving my voice and making a real difference, plus it's fulfilling in so many ways. It's just great, you know?memory keywords: []memory tags: ['general']
talk start time:12:09 am on 13 September, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : [Image: a photo of a painting of a heart on a table] I'm inspired seeing my work make a difference for the LGBTQ+ community. Knowing I'm helping create a more loving world is amazing. I'm really thankful for my friends, family and mentors' support. It inspires me to keep making art, too.memory context: Generalmemory keywords: []memory tags: ['inclusive', 'diverse', 'community', 'symbolism', 'emotional']
talk start time:4:33 pm on 12 July, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Hey Mel, great to chat with you again! So much has happened since we last spoke - I went to an LGBTQ conference two days ago and it was really special. I got the chance to meet and connect with people who've gone through similar journeys. It was such a welcoming environment and I felt totally accepted. I'm really thankful for this amazing community - it's shown me how important it is to fight for trans rights and spread awareness.memory context: I've been attending meetings and events, and it's been a fulfilling experience to see the positive changes we're making together. It's a great way to connect with like-minded individuals who share our values.memory keywords: []memory tags: ['general']
talk start time:8:56 pm on 20 July, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Hey Mel! A lot's happened since we last chatted - I just joined a new LGBTQ activist group last Tues. I'm meeting so many cool people who are as passionate as I am about rights and community support. I'm giving my voice and making a real difference, plus it's fulfilling in so many ways. It's just great, you know?memory context: I ran into a group of religious conservatives who said something that really upset me. It made me think how much work we still have to do for LGBTQ rights. It's been so helpful to have people around me who accept and support me, so I know I'll be ok!memory keywords: []memory tags: ['general']
talk start time:10:37 am on 27 June, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : I'm still figuring out the details, but I'm thinking of working with trans people, helping them accept themselves and supporting their mental health. Last Friday, I went to an LGBTQ+ counseling workshop and it was really enlightening. They talked about different therapeutic methods and how to best work with trans people. Seeing how passionate these pros were about making a safe space for people like me was amazing.memory context: Speaker Carolinesays : I'm still figuring out the details, but I'm thinking of working with trans people, helping them accept themselves and supporting their mental health. Last Friday, I went to an LGBTQ+ counseling workshop and it was really enlightening. They talked about different therapeutic methods and how to best work with trans people. Seeing how passionate these pros were about making a safe space for people like me was amazing.memory keywords: []memory tags: ['trans', 'growth']
